official-title.#text:
Providing for the appointment of Risa Lavizzo-Mourey as a citizen regent of the Board of Regents of
			 the Smithsonian Institution.

{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}enti.#tail:
, in the
			 class other than Members of Congress, occurring by reason of the
			 expiration of the term of Patricia Q. Stonesifer of Washington, DC, on
			 December 21, 2013, is filled by the appointment of Risa Lavizzo-Mourey of
			 Pennsylvania.	The appointment is for a term of 6 years, beginning on the
			 later of December 22, 2013, or the date of enactment of this joint
			 resolution.
